WEBVTT

00:01:35.359 --> 00:01:37.359
That's as much as three months of my salary.

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:39.079
I work my butt off.

00:01:39.079 --> 00:01:40.760
But it still can't keep up with how much you spend.

00:01:40.760 --> 00:01:41.799
Look at this trip of yours.

00:01:41.799 --> 00:01:43.239
A bag, flowers...

00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:44.159
About this bag...

00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:45.959
Hold on, I have another meeting.

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:48.000
We'll talk more when I get back.

00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:49.400
When will it end?

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:50.359
Not sure.

00:01:50.799 --> 00:01:51.680
When will you be back?

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:52.680
Hard to say.

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:55.400
"Not sure," "hard to say."

00:01:56.159 --> 00:01:57.480
Then what am I supposed to do?

00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:01.359
This section here...

00:02:01.359 --> 00:02:03.079
is the overall plan prepared

00:02:03.079 --> 00:02:05.079
by our colleagues in the operations department.

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:07.319
Next, regarding new media...

00:02:07.319 --> 00:02:09.520
There are a total of twenty-six short videos.

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:12.639
Thirteen of them require scripted content.

00:02:22.360 --> 00:02:23.840
What the heck did you write?

00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:25.520
Yes, it's my fault.

00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:27.199
It really is my fault.

00:02:34.360 --> 00:02:35.080
You have no idea...

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:37.080
The dirty stuff behind that promotion...

00:02:37.080 --> 00:02:38.360
I can't even be bothered to talk about it.

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:40.319
You talk as if I've never had a job.

00:02:40.479 --> 00:02:41.919
So my promotion and raise in Xi'an...

00:02:41.919 --> 00:02:43.159
were also through dirty means, right?

00:02:43.159 --> 00:02:44.280
No, no, no.

00:03:48.080 --> 00:03:50.520
When I was a kid, I was quite popular in the alley.

00:03:53.800 --> 00:03:55.960
The adults said I was delicate, like a girl.

00:03:58.960 --> 00:04:00.159
And because of this...

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:03.360
my old man was actually quite smug. He said...

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:05.960
"A man with feminine features is blessed."

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:06.960
When he grows up, he'll definitely...

00:04:31.720 --> 00:04:32.480
Getting some sun?

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:32.879
Yes.

00:04:33.519 --> 00:04:34.480
Nice weather today.

00:04:34.480 --> 00:04:35.000
Yes.

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:46.720
Hello?

00:04:47.279 --> 00:04:48.399
Hello, Third Uncle.

00:04:48.959 --> 00:04:51.079
So, I did what you said.

00:04:51.079 --> 00:04:52.160
I provoked him quite a bit.

00:04:52.680 --> 00:04:54.519
I saw his expression getting worse and worse.

00:04:54.519 --> 00:04:56.160
And he was baring his teeth, looking furious.

00:04:56.519 --> 00:04:57.720
I reckon...

00:04:57.720 --> 00:05:00.480
he's about to go after you for real now.

00:05:00.519 --> 00:05:01.480
Be careful.

00:05:01.959 --> 00:05:03.160
As long as he's willing to go all out...

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.079
I'll keep him company.

00:05:06.399 --> 00:05:07.360
Gotta go for now.

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:09.279
What's wrong?

00:05:10.399 --> 00:05:12.600
When exactly is that money supposed to arrive?

00:05:13.560 --> 00:05:14.879
You went to see Xiaoshi?

00:05:16.839 --> 00:05:18.079
That thing you said...

00:05:18.079 --> 00:05:20.399
about making Peng Le Xuan big within three months...

00:05:20.399 --> 00:05:23.079
and going public within two years... is it reliable or not?

00:05:23.399 --> 00:05:24.519
What did Xiaoshi do to you?

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:25.160
I...

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:32.399
Look at me, a Beijinger...

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:33.720
born and raised here...

00:05:33.839 --> 00:05:35.279
and I've achieved nothing so far.

00:05:35.519 --> 00:05:36.959
This time when I went to see my wife...

00:05:36.959 --> 00:05:37.959
She's now...

00:05:38.399 --> 00:05:39.800
valued by her leaders...

00:05:40.279 --> 00:05:41.279
with obedient staff.

00:05:41.399 --> 00:05:42.279
When she runs a meeting...

00:05:42.279 --> 00:05:43.519
the way she lays out grand plans...

00:05:43.519 --> 00:05:45.040
that spirited, confident look... I...

00:05:45.959 --> 00:05:46.720
I even feel...

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:47.399
if this continues...

00:05:47.399 --> 00:05:48.360
I won't be good enough for her anymore.

00:05:48.360 --> 00:05:49.959
I must get my career on track.

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:51.600
You're jealous of Xiaoshi.

00:05:52.839 --> 00:05:54.040
How could I be?

00:05:55.040 --> 00:05:56.040
That's a good thing too.

00:05:56.480 --> 00:05:58.399
As long as you're willing to come back and work steadily...

00:05:58.399 --> 00:05:58.959
That's good.

00:05:59.040 --> 00:06:00.040
So about this work of ours...

00:06:00.040 --> 00:06:01.600
when can we make progress?

00:06:03.399 --> 00:06:04.360
That depends on Big Brother.

00:06:04.360 --> 00:06:05.160
Depends on Big Brother.

00:06:05.160 --> 00:06:05.839
He's here.

00:06:05.839 --> 00:06:07.480
Big Brother, we were just talking about you.

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:09.600
Perfect, you're both here.

00:06:09.839 --> 00:06:11.319
I came over just to say...

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:13.720
I'm not doing the taste test.

00:06:14.040 --> 00:06:16.160
I'm not roasting duck anymore.

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:18.920
I'm not getting involved with the chef stuff either.

00:06:18.920 --> 00:06:22.360
I'm going to focus on studying our Feifei.

00:06:23.319 --> 00:06:24.399
What's going on now?

00:06:24.399 --> 00:06:25.120
Go check it out.

00:06:29.800 --> 00:06:31.759
Bro, what's this about?

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:36.480
Second Brother's here, perfect.

00:06:36.480 --> 00:06:38.600
Let me repeat what I just said.

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:40.240
From now on...

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:42.120
I'm just not making roast duck anymore.

00:06:44.319 --> 00:06:45.000
You...

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:46.199
Don't do that.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:47.600
I disagree.

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:49.560
Agree or not, I don't care.

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:50.879
Second Brother.

00:06:50.879 --> 00:06:52.000
We'll do it your way.

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:53.360
Find a ready-made chef.

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:54.920
I'll act as his consultant then.

00:06:56.759 --> 00:06:57.480
Big Brother...

00:06:57.879 --> 00:06:59.920
No, isn't that what you wanted all along?

00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:00.600
Right?

00:07:00.879 --> 00:07:01.920
We'll do as you say.

00:07:03.480 --> 00:07:04.759
I've figured it out too.

00:07:04.920 --> 00:07:05.759
Me...

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:08.920
Don't try to fool me anymore.

00:07:08.920 --> 00:07:10.560
I'm not doing this.

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:13.560
Alright then.

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:14.920
I'll handle the arrangements.

00:07:15.319 --> 00:07:16.560
What are you arranging?

00:07:16.560 --> 00:07:17.279
He's talking nonsense.

00:07:17.279 --> 00:07:17.920
I object.

00:07:21.279 --> 00:07:22.759
The reason I provoked you like that...

00:07:22.759 --> 00:07:24.399
was to make you focus on roasting duck properly.

00:07:24.839 --> 00:07:26.240
Now you just decide to quit?

00:07:26.600 --> 00:07:27.480
If you can't recreate...

00:07:27.480 --> 00:07:29.000
the old Peng Le Xuan flavor...

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:30.759
then I won't invest the money.

00:07:30.839 --> 00:07:31.920
Invest or not, suit yourself.

00:07:32.480 --> 00:07:33.000
Hey...

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:35.120
Can you not talk to Big Brother like that?

00:07:35.639 --> 00:07:37.879
You two, stop bickering like this.

00:07:37.879 --> 00:07:39.040
It's easy to create a deadlock.

00:07:41.240 --> 00:07:42.879
Bro, listen to me for a second.

00:07:42.879 --> 00:07:44.279
I think you should practice a bit more.

00:07:44.279 --> 00:07:46.040
Let's not let this whole thing fall apart, okay?

00:07:46.040 --> 00:07:47.000
Don't waste your breath on me.

00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:48.160
Hand me the tea.

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:49.240
The freshly brewed tea.

00:08:07.879 --> 00:08:10.480
Big Brother, Second Brother, listen to me.

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:11.920
Let's listen to Ma Weiguo on this.

00:08:11.920 --> 00:08:13.279
Right now, we're counting on him.

00:08:13.480 --> 00:08:14.839
We finally have a chance to turn things around.

00:08:14.839 --> 00:08:16.279
Let's not miss it, okay?

00:08:16.480 --> 00:08:19.120
Qiu'er, don't you worry.

00:08:19.879 --> 00:08:21.879
I actually have some good news to tell you.

00:08:21.879 --> 00:08:22.759
What good news?

00:08:22.759 --> 00:08:23.879
What's wrong, Weiguo?

00:08:24.040 --> 00:08:25.040
What's going on with you?

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:28.399
There's just a small issue.

00:08:32.039 --> 00:08:33.399
My funds have been frozen.

00:08:35.440 --> 00:08:37.200
No, no, sit, sit down and have some water.

00:08:40.120 --> 00:08:42.639
How did they suddenly... suddenly get frozen?

00:08:43.679 --> 00:08:44.799
What about Laise?

00:08:44.799 --> 00:08:47.519
They say they want to investigate a few of my past M&A cases.

00:08:47.679 --> 00:08:48.639
So...

00:08:48.639 --> 00:08:51.279
Inves... investigation...

00:08:51.279 --> 00:08:52.440
How long will that take?

00:08:52.639 --> 00:08:53.519
How long is the investigation?

00:08:53.519 --> 00:08:54.240
Over three months.

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:55.519
Over three months?!

00:08:57.639 --> 00:08:58.519
Well, that's it then.

00:08:58.519 --> 00:08:59.679
Our project is dead in the water again.

00:08:59.679 --> 00:09:00.519
He's bailing on us again.

00:09:00.519 --> 00:09:02.519
Don't worry, I'll handle it.

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:05.159
We'll proceed with the original plan.

00:09:05.519 --> 00:09:06.120
Big Brother.

00:09:06.279 --> 00:09:08.000
For these three months, you just keep practicing your skills.

00:09:08.399 --> 00:09:09.159
No need.

00:09:12.519 --> 00:09:13.679
I've already secured the money.

00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:19.279
The reason I came today...

00:09:19.279 --> 00:09:20.639
...is to announce this.

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:23.279
Ten million in cash.

00:09:24.279 --> 00:09:25.519
No due diligence required.

00:09:25.519 --> 00:09:27.240
And we don't have to put up with any more nonsense.

00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:29.399
And Big Brother doesn't need to practice his skills.

00:09:29.519 --> 00:09:30.919
The money can be transferred anytime.

00:09:31.240 --> 00:09:32.919
Why didn't you say so earlier?

00:09:32.919 --> 00:09:35.399
Should we open that bottle of wine now?

00:09:36.399 --> 00:09:38.120
Who would invest in you at a time like this?

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:41.679
That's none of your concern.

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:44.120
It has absolutely nothing to do with you.

00:09:44.519 --> 00:09:45.639
Since you can't come up with the money now...

00:09:45.639 --> 00:09:46.799
...you're already out of the game.

00:09:58.000 --> 00:09:58.799
Wait.

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:03.080
I remember we had a previous agreement, right?

00:10:03.399 --> 00:10:04.480
How did it go again?

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:05.879
I said...

00:10:06.159 --> 00:10:07.759
...I would personally invest in Peng Le Xuan.

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:09.159
Who believes that?

00:10:09.159 --> 00:10:10.000
Three months.

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:11.399
Within three months...

00:10:11.519 --> 00:10:14.279
...I'll double Peng Le Xuan's valuation to one hundred sixty million.

00:10:14.399 --> 00:10:16.279
You're a smart man too, right?

00:10:16.399 --> 00:10:18.559
You also know that under these circumstances...

00:10:18.759 --> 00:10:20.399
...Peng Le Xuan can go public very soon.

00:10:20.679 --> 00:10:23.039
Fine. If you manage it in three months...

00:10:23.039 --> 00:10:23.919
...I'll apologize to you.

00:10:23.919 --> 00:10:24.559
Deal.

00:10:24.799 --> 00:10:26.120
And if you can't do it?

00:10:26.120 --> 00:10:27.399
If I can't do it...

00:10:28.320 --> 00:10:29.879
...I'll apologize to the three of you.

00:10:29.879 --> 00:10:30.759
Within three months...

00:10:30.759 --> 00:10:32.600
...if you fail to make Peng Le Xuan a success...

00:10:32.840 --> 00:10:35.200
...you'll kowtow and admit your mistake to the three of us...

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:36.600
...and then get the hell out of the country.

00:10:36.759 --> 00:10:37.519
That was the deal, wasn't it?

00:10:37.519 --> 00:10:38.240
Second Brother.

00:10:38.240 --> 00:10:40.000
That was all just joking around at the time.

00:10:40.639 --> 00:10:41.600
Don't worry.

00:10:41.720 --> 00:10:43.759
I always keep my promises.

00:10:45.519 --> 00:10:47.519
Besides, the three months aren't up yet.

00:10:47.759 --> 00:10:50.480
Fine. I'll be waiting to settle the score.

00:10:50.639 --> 00:10:52.519
You don't have much time left.

00:10:52.840 --> 00:10:53.720
Second Brother.

00:10:58.720 --> 00:10:59.960
What's going on here?

00:11:00.320 --> 00:11:01.320
Another conversation blew up.

00:11:02.440 --> 00:11:03.320
It's nothing.

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:04.720
Just the game leveling up.

00:11:05.559 --> 00:11:06.799
Didn't you say you'd take me...

00:11:06.799 --> 00:11:08.360
...to Panjiayuan to browse for props? Let's go.

00:11:09.159 --> 00:11:10.879
I'm pretty busy today. Next time.

00:11:11.720 --> 00:11:12.559
Again?

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:14.679
With an attitude like that, you'll never win this game.

00:11:18.799 --> 00:11:19.960
Do you believe in the light?

00:11:22.080 --> 00:11:23.159
Are you crazy?

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:32.679
You... you think...

00:11:32.679 --> 00:11:34.320
He, he, he... he couldn't be...

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:35.799
...involved in some serious trouble, could he?

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:39.440
Whatever trouble he's in...

00:11:39.440 --> 00:11:40.960
...is also because of that mouth of his.

00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:43.799
Just think how many people he must have offended with that mouth.

00:11:43.840 --> 00:11:46.080
He definitely offended plenty of people abroad too.

00:11:46.799 --> 00:11:47.799
Alright, alright.

00:11:47.799 --> 00:11:48.799
Let's not talk about him for now.

00:11:49.080 --> 00:11:51.559
Our investment funds are arriving soon.

00:11:51.559 --> 00:11:53.080
Shouldn't we celebrate?

00:11:53.320 --> 00:11:54.559
What do you guys want to eat later?

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:57.559
Hold on, where did this money come from?

00:11:57.840 --> 00:11:58.679
Yeah.

00:11:59.440 --> 00:12:00.720
Before, it was so hard to borrow money.

00:12:00.720 --> 00:12:01.799
Now it just appears out of nowhere.

00:12:01.799 --> 00:12:03.200
And the terms are so good.

00:12:04.559 --> 00:12:05.799
A friend.

00:12:06.440 --> 00:12:07.600
What kind of friend?

00:12:08.039 --> 00:12:09.480
What friend is that generous?

00:12:11.080 --> 00:12:12.799
It came through legitimate means, anyway.

00:12:12.840 --> 00:12:14.120
I guarantee it's clean.

00:12:24.840 --> 00:12:26.480
How many years have we been building Laise together?

00:12:26.600 --> 00:12:27.519
Ten years.

00:12:28.720 --> 00:12:29.879
And how long have I been gone?

00:12:30.440 --> 00:12:31.279
One month.

00:12:32.440 --> 00:12:33.879
I thought it had been several years.

00:12:35.600 --> 00:12:37.759
While it's true that when a man leaves, the tea grows cold...

00:12:37.759 --> 00:12:39.759
...you didn't need to move against me so hastily.

00:12:39.960 --> 00:12:41.360
What do you mean by that?

00:12:41.360 --> 00:12:42.759
I genuinely don't understand.

00:12:43.960 --> 00:12:45.480
Those M&A cases...

00:12:45.480 --> 00:12:47.360
...were completely clean, without any issues.

00:12:47.480 --> 00:12:51.120
Accusing me of privately taking shares, accepting bribes...

00:12:51.120 --> 00:12:52.600
...backroom deals, and so on.

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:53.960
That was all on your orders, wasn't it?

00:12:54.120 --> 00:12:55.480
This is a misunderstanding.

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:57.480
We've been partners for so many years.

00:12:57.759 --> 00:12:59.360
How could I not trust you?

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:02.559
But someone really did report and expose this.

00:13:03.080 --> 00:13:04.600
The procedures have to be followed.

00:13:04.600 --> 00:13:06.000
This is also the management regulation...

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:08.480
...that we both established back then, right?

00:13:09.960 --> 00:13:11.480
You've been waiting for this opportunity for a long time, haven't you?

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:15.679
Old Ma, let me put it to you this way.

00:13:16.840 --> 00:13:18.720
I can assure you...

00:13:19.840 --> 00:13:22.960
...this matter has absolutely nothing to do with me.

00:13:23.120 --> 00:13:24.000
You can rest assured.

00:13:24.480 --> 00:13:26.000
It's just a procedural matter.

00:13:26.000 --> 00:13:26.759
Okay?

00:13:26.840 --> 00:13:30.000
Also, if you're having cash flow problems on your end...

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:31.600
...please don't hesitate to ask me.

00:13:33.320 --> 00:13:35.000
That won't be necessary. Thank you.

00:13:55.039 --> 00:13:56.000
Hello, Martin.

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:56.840
Wang Esq.

00:13:56.960 --> 00:13:58.000
How's it going over there?

00:13:58.759 --> 00:14:00.720
The situation is very tricky now.

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:02.639
We need to call in some favors now.

00:14:02.639 --> 00:14:03.559
And,

00:14:04.279 --> 00:14:07.080
we also need to halt some business collaborations.

00:14:07.080 --> 00:14:08.960
This matter is a bit complicated at the moment.

00:14:09.360 --> 00:14:11.960
I'm currently trying to solve it with various plans.

00:14:12.039 --> 00:14:12.840
So,

00:14:13.159 --> 00:14:14.679
please give me a little more time.

00:14:14.679 --> 00:14:15.799
I'll handle it.

00:14:16.360 --> 00:14:17.200
Sorry for the trouble.

00:14:17.200 --> 00:14:18.120
As soon as possible.

00:14:34.679 --> 00:14:36.240
How are things on your end?

00:14:36.320 --> 00:14:38.240
Is there anything we can help with?

00:14:38.240 --> 00:14:39.000
Say something.

00:14:39.600 --> 00:14:40.639
What's it to you?

00:14:41.759 --> 00:14:43.000
Still angry?

00:14:43.240 --> 00:14:44.919
It's not that I'm not on your side.

00:14:44.919 --> 00:14:46.759
I really need a career right now.

00:14:47.159 --> 00:14:47.879
Anything else?

00:15:00.679 --> 00:15:02.720
What you guys did wasn't very decent.

00:15:03.159 --> 00:15:05.759
Weiguo is, after all, one of our own brothers.

00:15:06.639 --> 00:15:07.879
What brother?

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:12.240
He scolded us like we were his grandsons.

00:15:15.240 --> 00:15:16.480
It's so hot.

00:15:17.000 --> 00:15:18.440
Let it cool for a bit.

00:15:19.240 --> 00:15:20.720
Didn't you see him going off on me?

00:15:21.240 --> 00:15:23.000
He went off on me so hard I was gasping.

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:24.919
Besides,

00:15:24.919 --> 00:15:27.000
it wasn't me who drove him away, right?

00:15:29.639 --> 00:15:32.320
Anyway, it's what you wanted now.

00:15:32.519 --> 00:15:33.799
How is it what I wanted?

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:35.159
We have the money.

00:15:35.480 --> 00:15:37.879
You don't have to practice roasting ducks anymore.

00:15:38.000 --> 00:15:38.639
Right?

00:15:40.519 --> 00:15:42.240
No, I mean, Peng Le Xuan can't just

00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:44.399
sit idle all day long, right?

00:15:44.639 --> 00:15:45.399
Now that we have money,

00:15:45.399 --> 00:15:47.159
we can get it on track, can't we?

00:15:49.200 --> 00:15:52.639
But why don't you seem happy?

00:15:53.279 --> 00:15:55.039
Still worried about Weiguo, huh?

00:15:55.799 --> 00:15:57.600
Me, worry about him?

00:15:58.480 --> 00:16:00.240
I'm overjoyed.

00:16:00.320 --> 00:16:02.840
Let him taste what it's like to have no money.

00:16:06.799 --> 00:16:08.840
Yeah, you're right.

00:16:10.360 --> 00:16:11.120
Happy.

00:16:14.360 --> 00:16:16.879
Soaking? How long do we wait for it to cool?

00:17:09.119 --> 00:17:10.599
Stop spraying! Stop!

00:17:10.599 --> 00:17:12.960
It's me! It hurts so much!

00:17:14.119 --> 00:17:15.359
Li Lianbao?

00:17:16.160 --> 00:17:17.400
It's me!

00:17:18.559 --> 00:17:19.960
What are you doing here?

00:17:19.960 --> 00:17:21.640
I was waiting for you.

00:17:22.359 --> 00:17:23.920
What did you spray on me?

00:17:25.960 --> 00:17:26.720
Waiting for me?

00:17:26.720 --> 00:17:28.359
You scared me to death!

00:17:29.559 --> 00:17:30.559
Are you okay?

00:17:34.960 --> 00:17:35.759
Don't move, don't move.

00:17:39.359 --> 00:17:39.960
Over here.

00:17:43.880 --> 00:17:45.359
Relax, relax.

00:17:45.359 --> 00:17:45.960
Here.

00:17:48.680 --> 00:17:49.599
Feeling better?

00:17:53.039 --> 00:17:54.119
You're still laughing?

00:17:54.799 --> 00:17:56.400
You were way too rough.

00:17:56.720 --> 00:17:57.799
You didn't even see who it was.

00:17:57.799 --> 00:17:58.960
You just started spraying.

00:17:59.559 --> 00:18:01.599
No, but you, in the middle of the night,

00:18:01.599 --> 00:18:03.119
hiding in our building's stairwell...

00:18:03.160 --> 00:18:05.119
How was I supposed to know you weren't a creep?

00:18:05.119 --> 00:18:07.079
It's good I didn't call the police on you.

00:18:07.319 --> 00:18:08.720
I called you, you didn't answer.

00:18:08.839 --> 00:18:10.440
I texted you on WeChat, you didn't reply.

00:18:10.640 --> 00:18:11.799
So I had to come see

00:18:11.799 --> 00:18:13.200
what was going on.

00:18:13.200 --> 00:18:14.200
But when I got here,

00:18:14.200 --> 00:18:15.519
I rang the bell, no one answered.

00:18:15.640 --> 00:18:17.480
No, where's your housekeeper?

00:18:17.480 --> 00:18:18.359
Where did she go?

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:23.359
We had meetings at the company all afternoon.

00:18:23.359 --> 00:18:24.839
My phone was on silent.

00:18:25.279 --> 00:18:27.039
My housekeeper took the day off today.

00:18:27.240 --> 00:18:29.240
I sent Xuanxuan to my parents' place.

00:18:36.920 --> 00:18:37.960
But you,

00:18:38.720 --> 00:18:40.880
what are you doing at my place so late?

00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:42.240
I'm in a bad mood.

00:18:42.240 --> 00:18:43.359
I want to pick a fight.

00:18:45.039 --> 00:18:46.480
Are you crazy, Li Lianbao?

00:18:47.359 --> 00:18:48.960
Anyway, I just wanted to find someone

00:18:48.960 --> 00:18:51.079
I really can't stand and have a huge fight.

00:18:51.200 --> 00:18:52.240
And face-to-face.

00:18:52.240 --> 00:18:53.279
Someone I can out-argue.

00:18:53.960 --> 00:18:55.240
You're nuts.

00:18:58.720 --> 00:18:59.880
You're insane.

00:19:04.400 --> 00:19:06.119
I kicked Ma Weiguo out.

00:19:09.400 --> 00:19:10.640
So you came to my place

00:19:10.640 --> 00:19:11.880
to set your sights on me?

00:19:13.599 --> 00:19:15.000
What are you thinking?

00:19:15.720 --> 00:19:17.200
I found someone to take over.

00:19:18.519 --> 00:19:19.319
Who?

00:19:21.799 --> 00:19:22.519
Kevin.

00:19:23.400 --> 00:19:24.720
Haven't you always wanted

00:19:24.720 --> 00:19:26.440
shares in Hive Tech?

00:19:26.720 --> 00:19:27.400
Okay.

00:19:28.079 --> 00:19:29.880
Tom, you've finally come around.

00:19:31.119 --> 00:19:31.960
Name your price.

00:19:32.359 --> 00:19:33.480
The price is negotiable.

00:19:33.839 --> 00:19:35.160
But I have one condition.

00:19:35.880 --> 00:19:36.720
Go ahead.

00:19:37.720 --> 00:19:39.359
You must invest in Peng Le Xuan.

00:19:39.599 --> 00:19:40.359
Tom,

00:19:40.400 --> 00:19:42.960
you know I never invest in food service projects.

00:19:43.039 --> 00:19:44.319
That's not my field.

00:19:44.640 --> 00:19:45.960
But,

00:19:46.400 --> 00:19:49.400
for you, I'm willing.

00:19:50.839 --> 00:19:52.480
Don't be so mushy, okay?

00:19:52.640 --> 00:19:54.119
But I have to make it clear,

00:19:54.519 --> 00:19:55.680
I'm not begging you.

00:19:56.119 --> 00:19:57.480
This is just a form of cooperation.

00:19:58.119 --> 00:19:58.839
Fine.

00:19:59.640 --> 00:20:01.759
But my investment also has requirements.

00:20:02.000 --> 00:20:04.079
I knew you weren't a good guy either.

00:20:04.599 --> 00:20:06.200
Alright, then let's talk.

00:20:09.960 --> 00:20:12.039
Do you think I'm utterly shameless?

00:20:12.440 --> 00:20:14.240
Actually going to ask Lao Kai for money.

00:20:16.720 --> 00:20:18.640
If you want to laugh at me,

00:20:18.720 --> 00:20:19.720
go ahead and do it.

00:20:32.119 --> 00:20:34.799
Alright, I'm leaving.

00:20:37.640 --> 00:20:38.279
Apply it.

00:20:40.359 --> 00:20:42.400
I just think you men...

00:20:42.400 --> 00:20:43.240
are childish.

00:20:43.759 --> 00:20:45.440
Things like "stealing my wife"...

00:20:45.440 --> 00:20:46.799
or "snatching your daughter"...

00:20:46.960 --> 00:20:48.359
What era is this?

00:20:48.519 --> 00:20:50.000
He even fired me.

00:20:50.319 --> 00:20:52.160
Now you know why I don't think much of you.

00:20:53.000 --> 00:20:54.200
You, as a person...

00:20:54.200 --> 00:20:56.359
are usually quite shameless...

00:20:56.640 --> 00:20:58.880
but I've found you do have a bottom line.

00:20:59.200 --> 00:21:00.160
Let me put it this way.

00:21:00.200 --> 00:21:02.240
If Weiguo were in your place...

00:21:02.440 --> 00:21:04.799
do you think he'd hesitate...

00:21:04.799 --> 00:21:06.279
about taking Kevin's money?

00:21:06.880 --> 00:21:08.440
Probably not.

00:21:08.440 --> 00:21:09.799
Definitely not.

00:21:10.599 --> 00:21:12.440
As long as he can secure investment...

00:21:12.440 --> 00:21:14.400
as long as he can achieve his goal...

00:21:14.400 --> 00:21:16.720
he'd charge ahead without a second thought.

00:21:16.720 --> 00:21:17.960
But you wouldn't.

00:21:18.359 --> 00:21:19.960
In daily life...

00:21:19.960 --> 00:21:21.640
having principles is a virtue.

00:21:21.720 --> 00:21:23.359
But in business...

00:21:23.359 --> 00:21:25.079
that's your biggest flaw.

00:21:28.480 --> 00:21:31.440
Fine, I'll take that as a compliment.

00:21:33.240 --> 00:21:34.519
How rare.

00:21:34.640 --> 00:21:36.200
To hear such words...

00:21:36.200 --> 00:21:37.200
from someone as ungrateful as you.

00:21:37.240 --> 00:21:38.880
Are you asking for another spray?

00:21:39.200 --> 00:21:39.880
No.

00:21:40.799 --> 00:21:43.079
Couldn't you tell it was me earlier?

00:21:43.880 --> 00:21:45.720
It was so dark, and I was scared.

00:21:45.720 --> 00:21:47.720
How was I supposed to recognize you?

00:21:47.720 --> 00:21:49.799
See? That's exactly what being ungrateful is.

00:21:51.359 --> 00:21:52.359
Don't you forget...

00:21:52.359 --> 00:21:53.480
back in eighth grade...

00:21:54.279 --> 00:21:55.960
during P.E., you sprained your ankle.

00:21:55.960 --> 00:21:57.960
Who carried you to the infirmary?

00:21:58.559 --> 00:21:59.640
You were on my back...

00:21:59.640 --> 00:22:01.240
snot and tears all over my neck.

00:22:02.960 --> 00:22:04.640
You have the nerve to bring that up?

00:22:04.799 --> 00:22:06.960
You didn't even make it to the infirmary.

00:22:07.240 --> 00:22:08.640
You took a huge tumble.

00:22:08.880 --> 00:22:10.480
I only had a sprained ankle...

00:22:10.480 --> 00:22:12.160
but then my hand got fractured.

00:22:13.240 --> 00:22:14.720
It's because you were so heavy!

00:22:16.119 --> 00:22:16.960
It's all your fault.

00:22:17.119 --> 00:22:19.119
I had to rest at home for half a month.

00:22:19.359 --> 00:22:21.200
Missed two weeks of classes.

00:22:21.720 --> 00:22:24.039
I didn't even get first place in the midterms.

00:22:24.640 --> 00:22:25.480
You know what?

00:22:25.480 --> 00:22:27.559
That was the only time I ever came in second.

00:22:28.119 --> 00:22:28.759
Wait...

00:22:29.119 --> 00:22:30.960
I brought you the class notes.

00:22:31.599 --> 00:22:32.799
I just didn't dare go inside.

00:22:33.119 --> 00:22:34.359
I was afraid your dad would beat me up.

00:22:34.720 --> 00:22:36.119
I left them by the door.

00:22:36.240 --> 00:22:37.400
Didn't you get them?

00:22:38.720 --> 00:22:40.920
Later, I even brought you a soda when I came back.

00:22:41.240 --> 00:22:42.559
I never got to drink it.

00:22:43.160 --> 00:22:44.160
I drank it.

00:22:45.720 --> 00:22:46.920
What kind of person does that?

00:22:47.119 --> 00:22:49.799
But didn't Lili buy you a popsicle back then?

00:22:50.200 --> 00:22:52.960
You were so happy you had snot bubbles.

00:22:52.960 --> 00:22:54.960
I was afraid you'd choke on the soda.

00:22:55.160 --> 00:22:58.359
No, Lili liked Ma Weiguo.

00:22:58.519 --> 00:23:00.759
She asked me to pass a message for her.

00:23:01.000 --> 00:23:02.480
Where did you get that idea?

00:23:03.039 --> 00:23:03.880
Really.

00:23:07.240 --> 00:23:09.839
It sounds to me like you were jealous.

00:23:10.960 --> 00:23:12.279
Me? Jealous?

00:23:12.480 --> 00:23:13.799
What a joke.

00:23:13.960 --> 00:23:15.200
Back then, the people chasing me...

00:23:15.200 --> 00:23:16.799
couldn't even fit in Tiananmen Square.

00:23:17.599 --> 00:23:18.720
And you think *I* was jealous?

00:23:18.720 --> 00:23:19.960
Yes, yes, yes.

00:23:20.240 --> 00:23:21.759
You were the hot commodity.

00:23:21.920 --> 00:23:23.400
*I* was the one who ate a lot of vinegar.

00:23:27.039 --> 00:23:28.279
You were jealous?

00:23:29.960 --> 00:23:31.240
You were jealous?

00:23:31.519 --> 00:23:33.039
Why did you never tell me...

00:23:33.039 --> 00:23:35.440
I was afraid of holding back your studies.

00:23:36.960 --> 00:23:38.559
You were so competitive.

00:23:38.759 --> 00:23:39.440
Coming in second...

00:23:39.440 --> 00:23:40.759
was like the sky falling for you.

00:23:43.279 --> 00:23:44.599
I originally planned...

00:23:44.759 --> 00:23:46.079
to tell you after the college entrance exams...

00:23:47.759 --> 00:23:48.960
But who would've thought...

00:23:48.960 --> 00:23:50.599
that fight happened.

00:23:51.079 --> 00:23:53.000
My guaranteed admission to Beihang University fell through.

00:23:53.400 --> 00:23:54.880
I felt too ashamed.

00:23:56.039 --> 00:23:58.440
It's all Ma Weiguo's fault.

00:24:03.400 --> 00:24:05.400
My eye is starting to hurt again.

00:24:05.720 --> 00:24:06.720
What did you spray on me?

00:24:06.720 --> 00:24:07.799
Don't use your hands.

00:24:07.960 --> 00:24:08.720
Lie down.

00:24:10.160 --> 00:24:11.319
Lie down.

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:14.359
So direct?

00:24:16.319 --> 00:24:17.000
Okay, okay.

00:24:28.000 --> 00:24:29.759
If my eyes are ruined...

00:24:29.960 --> 00:24:31.960
you'll have to take care of me for the rest of my life.

00:24:32.039 --> 00:24:34.039
I'll see you off to your grave, that's how I'll take care of you.

00:24:34.039 --> 00:24:35.200
Forget it then.

00:24:35.720 --> 00:24:37.920
I'm afraid you'd scatter my ashes to the wind.

00:24:38.960 --> 00:24:39.960
Are you going to put the drops in or not?

00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:40.960
Yes, yes, yes.

00:24:42.000 --> 00:24:43.200
So much talk.

00:24:59.000 --> 00:24:59.960
What are you doing?

00:25:00.279 --> 00:25:01.240
Nothing.

00:25:01.960 --> 00:25:03.519
If it's nothing, why are you holding me?

00:25:05.039 --> 00:25:07.079
You didn't refuse either.

00:25:07.720 --> 00:25:09.200
I'm refusing now.

00:25:09.720 --> 00:25:10.759
Too late.

00:25:11.200 --> 00:25:12.160
Hurry up.

00:25:12.240 --> 00:25:13.440
What's wrong with you?

00:25:13.599 --> 00:25:14.799
I'm a patient now.

00:25:14.799 --> 00:25:15.160
What?

00:25:15.160 --> 00:25:16.480
Shouldn't you take good care of me?

00:25:17.920 --> 00:25:18.319
No.

00:25:18.319 --> 00:25:18.960
Let go of me.

00:25:18.960 --> 00:25:20.000
Be gentle.

00:25:21.200 --> 00:25:22.400
Don't bite me.

00:25:23.119 --> 00:25:24.319
Are you letting go or not?

00:25:57.400 --> 00:25:58.200
Stop pretending.

00:26:02.119 --> 00:26:02.920
Awake?

00:26:46.680 --> 00:26:47.480
I'm busy.

00:26:50.519 --> 00:26:51.400
So...

00:26:52.039 --> 00:26:54.160
Later, when Peng Le Xuan officially opens...

00:26:54.200 --> 00:26:55.200
I'll invite you to visit.

00:26:55.440 --> 00:26:57.279
I don't think that day will ever come.

00:26:58.559 --> 00:26:59.480
What do you mean?

00:27:02.160 --> 00:27:03.640
Obviously, I don't have high hopes for you.

00:27:04.480 --> 00:27:05.079
No, you...

00:27:11.960 --> 00:27:12.519
I'm leaving.

00:27:13.720 --> 00:27:15.599
Take that bag of stuff down with you.

00:27:19.720 --> 00:27:21.200
I'll buy you a new set later.

00:27:21.200 --> 00:27:22.200
No need.

00:27:23.000 --> 00:27:23.799
Goodbye.

00:27:52.599 --> 00:27:53.400
Martin

00:27:53.519 --> 00:27:54.720
Regarding your illness,

00:27:54.720 --> 00:27:56.480
I have already disclosed it to the investigators.

00:27:56.480 --> 00:27:58.480
I'm also applying to unfreeze some assets

00:27:58.480 --> 00:27:59.480
for medical expenses.

00:27:59.799 --> 00:28:01.240
Don't rush back yet.

00:28:01.400 --> 00:28:02.720
We need them to accept

00:28:02.720 --> 00:28:04.000
that you selling your house

00:28:04.000 --> 00:28:05.960
to get cash and return is for treatment,

00:28:06.039 --> 00:28:07.279
not to transfer assets.

00:28:07.279 --> 00:28:08.720
Okay, I understand.

00:28:09.240 --> 00:28:10.519
What's the next step?

00:28:10.799 --> 00:28:12.000
I'll wait for your further instructions.

00:28:12.480 --> 00:28:14.200
You must try to show

00:28:14.200 --> 00:28:16.720
that you are currently in a critical phase of treatment

00:28:16.960 --> 00:28:18.200
and cannot travel easily.

00:28:18.200 --> 00:28:19.359
Do you understand?

00:28:19.640 --> 00:28:20.240
Okay.

00:28:35.759 --> 00:28:36.720
Second Brother.

00:28:36.720 --> 00:28:39.160
You went to so much trouble, even prepared a fruit platter.

00:28:40.079 --> 00:28:42.720
I'm just balancing a relaxed and serious atmosphere.

00:28:42.720 --> 00:28:43.920
S-Second Brother is very, very thorough.

00:28:43.920 --> 00:28:45.200
It's just that eating watermelon first thing in the morning

00:28:45.200 --> 00:28:46.240
can easily upset your stomach.

00:28:46.440 --> 00:28:47.279
You're always the one with issues.

00:28:47.279 --> 00:28:47.960
How annoying.

00:28:47.960 --> 00:28:48.759
Don't talk nonsense.

00:28:48.759 --> 00:28:49.960
Let me make an announcement.

00:28:50.279 --> 00:28:52.200
Our future Peng Le Xuan account

00:28:52.200 --> 00:28:53.799
will be set up at Qiu'er's bank.

00:28:54.240 --> 00:28:55.000
See?

00:28:55.000 --> 00:28:55.720
Look at that.

00:28:55.720 --> 00:28:57.720
The investment funds are also arriving in batches.

00:28:57.759 --> 00:28:59.400
Qiu'er, you're responsible for this.

00:28:59.400 --> 00:29:00.480
Count it as your performance.

00:29:01.519 --> 00:29:02.240
So fast?

00:29:02.240 --> 00:29:03.880
Your Second Brother is looking out for you.

00:29:04.160 --> 00:29:04.759
Yes, yes, yes.

00:29:04.759 --> 00:29:05.599
Grateful to Second Brother.

00:29:05.599 --> 00:29:06.440
A heart full of gratitude.

00:29:08.200 --> 00:29:09.200
Starting today,

00:29:09.200 --> 00:29:10.200
we will proceed according to plan

00:29:10.200 --> 00:29:11.759
to truly build up Peng Le Xuan.

00:29:11.759 --> 00:29:12.400
Great.

00:29:12.799 --> 00:29:13.480
Today

00:29:13.480 --> 00:29:15.039
marks the first shareholders' meeting

00:29:15.039 --> 00:29:16.799
of our Peng Le Xuan

00:29:16.799 --> 00:29:18.279
Catering Co., Ltd.

00:29:20.559 --> 00:29:22.240
Wow, and we're even applauding.

00:29:23.640 --> 00:29:24.400
Big Brother.

00:29:25.160 --> 00:29:25.759
Sister-in-law.

00:29:27.160 --> 00:29:29.119
Shareholders' meeting charter.

00:29:29.119 --> 00:29:31.000
This is set up quite formally.

00:29:31.559 --> 00:29:33.240
We are now seriously running a business.

00:29:33.240 --> 00:29:35.000
It's not the small-time stuff from before.

00:29:35.160 --> 00:29:36.880
So, legal procedures,

00:29:36.880 --> 00:29:38.119
financial procedures, management procedures,

00:29:38.119 --> 00:29:38.960
and so on...

00:29:39.079 --> 00:29:42.119
All of this must have strict rules and regulations.

00:29:42.519 --> 00:29:44.160
And we must all comply.

00:29:44.160 --> 00:29:45.640
No one gets special privileges.

00:29:46.119 --> 00:29:47.640
No problem, we must comply.

00:29:48.720 --> 00:29:50.440
Now, I will announce

00:29:50.440 --> 00:29:52.920
the company's official appointments.

00:29:53.039 --> 00:29:54.440
I, Li Lianbao,

00:29:54.599 --> 00:29:57.400
will serve as the General Manager

00:29:57.400 --> 00:29:58.440
of Peng Le Xuan Catering Co., Ltd.

00:29:58.759 --> 00:30:00.519
I'm responsible for the restaurant's overall operations.

00:30:00.680 --> 00:30:02.640
All the worrying matters are mine.

00:30:02.680 --> 00:30:03.480
Hard work, hard work.

00:30:03.480 --> 00:30:04.240
Manager Li, you're working hard.

00:30:04.240 --> 00:30:04.920
It's my duty.

00:30:04.920 --> 00:30:06.440
Manager Li, thank you for your hard work.

00:30:06.440 --> 00:30:07.200
Tong Qiu,

00:30:07.279 --> 00:30:09.680
you will serve as Vice General Manager.

00:30:09.680 --> 00:30:12.680
You're responsible for business expansion

00:30:12.680 --> 00:30:14.440
and customer relations.

00:30:14.440 --> 00:30:15.279
No problem, right?

00:30:15.519 --> 00:30:17.440
Thank you for the company's trust in me.

00:30:17.440 --> 00:30:19.000
I will definitely fulfill my duties diligently.

00:30:19.000 --> 00:30:20.119
Work hard.

00:30:20.920 --> 00:30:21.759
Li Jing.

00:30:22.400 --> 00:30:23.160
Sister-in-law.

00:30:23.519 --> 00:30:25.799
You will serve as the restaurant's Lobby Manager.

00:30:26.559 --> 00:30:27.960
Wh-What about me?

00:30:27.960 --> 00:30:29.160
Of course.

00:30:29.400 --> 00:30:30.119
Sister-in-law,

00:30:30.640 --> 00:30:31.880
for so many years, Peng Le Xuan

00:30:31.880 --> 00:30:33.680
has relied on you managing everything inside and out.

00:30:33.680 --> 00:30:35.920
You know Peng Le Xuan best and have the most experience.

00:30:35.920 --> 00:30:37.720
This position is perfect for you.

00:30:37.759 --> 00:30:40.119
Second Brother, I will definitely work hard.

00:30:40.640 --> 00:30:41.200
Sister-in-law,

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:42.200
I, I suggest

00:30:42.200 --> 00:30:44.240
that from now on during meetings, we be more formal.

00:30:44.400 --> 00:30:45.319
Call me Manager Li.

00:30:45.599 --> 00:30:48.839
Alright, Manager Li, I will definitely work hard.

00:30:49.000 --> 00:30:49.839
Look at you.

00:30:51.559 --> 00:30:52.640
Wang Chunsheng.

00:30:52.640 --> 00:30:53.440
No, no.

00:30:53.440 --> 00:30:54.720
Second Brother, I know.

00:30:55.000 --> 00:30:58.440
I'll just be the head chef.

00:30:58.559 --> 00:31:00.680
I'll mainly act as an advisor for everyone.

00:31:01.240 --> 00:31:02.200
No, no, no.

00:31:02.680 --> 00:31:03.440
Big Brother.

00:31:03.599 --> 00:31:05.440
You will serve as the Chairman

00:31:05.440 --> 00:31:08.240
of Peng Le Xuan Catering Co., Ltd.

00:31:09.240 --> 00:31:10.680
You're an official now.

00:31:10.680 --> 00:31:12.920
No, what does this Chair... Chairman

00:31:12.920 --> 00:31:14.200
even do?

00:31:14.200 --> 00:31:15.480
Big Brother, don't worry.

00:31:15.480 --> 00:31:16.200
As for the Chairman,

00:31:16.200 --> 00:31:17.640
just be... be sensible.

00:31:18.440 --> 00:31:19.240
No, seriously.

00:31:19.240 --> 00:31:19.720
Big Brother.

00:31:19.720 --> 00:31:21.920
You truly are the perfect candidate for Chairman.

00:31:21.920 --> 00:31:24.039
I'd like to be it, but I'm not qualified, right?

00:31:24.039 --> 00:31:26.079
I can't be any Chairman.

00:31:26.079 --> 00:31:26.839
Big Brother.

00:31:27.000 --> 00:31:28.839
You've managed Peng Le Xuan for so many years.

00:31:28.839 --> 00:31:30.119
The Chairman position

00:31:30.119 --> 00:31:31.119
is perfect for you.

00:31:31.119 --> 00:31:32.039
That's right.

00:31:32.359 --> 00:31:33.160
Isn't it?

00:31:34.720 --> 00:31:36.319
Th-th-then I'll just

00:31:36.319 --> 00:31:38.279
be this "Sensible" Chairman.

00:31:38.519 --> 00:31:40.319
Don't worry, I'll definitely be sensible, okay?

00:31:40.319 --> 00:31:41.319
Yes, yes, yes.

00:31:42.960 --> 00:31:44.920
"Sensible" Chairman.

00:31:46.400 --> 00:31:47.759
Big Brother, here's yours.

00:31:48.200 --> 00:31:49.319
Even business cards?

00:31:49.400 --> 00:31:50.119
Sister-in-law,

00:31:50.119 --> 00:31:52.799
See how Second Brother does things? So proper.

00:31:52.839 --> 00:31:54.400
I had these business cards

00:31:54.400 --> 00:31:55.880
specially printed for everyone.

00:31:56.240 --> 00:31:57.920
Since we're running a business,

00:31:57.920 --> 00:31:59.359
we all have to be professional.

00:31:59.480 --> 00:32:00.119
Right.

00:32:15.400 --> 00:32:16.559
Let's meet up.

00:32:18.599 --> 00:32:20.279
Haven't you always wanted Peng Le Xuan?

00:32:20.599 --> 00:32:21.519
I can help you.

00:32:22.519 --> 00:32:23.400
I think...

00:32:23.400 --> 00:32:25.839
Our Peng Le Xuan must be renovated.

00:32:25.839 --> 00:32:27.880
So, big brother, sister-in-law,

00:32:28.200 --> 00:32:29.519
the room you're living in now

00:32:29.519 --> 00:32:30.759
must be vacated.

00:32:32.519 --> 00:32:35.400
Then where will our family of three live?

00:32:35.920 --> 00:32:37.160
No, think about it.

00:32:37.319 --> 00:32:39.720
The Chairman's family living in the restaurant

00:32:39.920 --> 00:32:42.640
is completely inconsistent with our company's image.

00:32:42.640 --> 00:32:43.319
That's true.

00:32:44.000 --> 00:32:45.319
But don't worry.

00:32:45.640 --> 00:32:46.839
The apartment...

00:32:46.839 --> 00:32:48.319
I've already rented one for you.

00:32:48.519 --> 00:32:49.480
Two bedrooms.

00:32:50.519 --> 00:32:52.599
The rent will be covered by the company.

00:32:52.759 --> 00:32:53.759
It's not far from here.

00:32:53.759 --> 00:32:54.599
After the meeting,

00:32:54.599 --> 00:32:55.519
I'll take you to see it.

00:32:55.519 --> 00:32:56.279
No, listen...

00:32:56.279 --> 00:32:58.359
Moving is a huge hassle.

00:32:58.359 --> 00:33:00.160
All our old stuff from decades,

00:33:00.160 --> 00:33:00.960
it may not be valuable,

00:33:00.960 --> 00:33:03.160
but it's a pain to pack up.

00:33:03.160 --> 00:33:04.799
Just look at our place...

00:33:04.799 --> 00:33:06.799
I'll help you pack.

00:33:07.279 --> 00:33:07.880
Think about it.

00:33:07.880 --> 00:33:09.960
How inconvenient was our old place?

00:33:09.960 --> 00:33:11.160
We lived in the outer room,

00:33:11.160 --> 00:33:13.160
and just pulled a curtain when the kid came in or out.

00:33:13.160 --> 00:33:14.119
I'm telling you,

00:33:14.119 --> 00:33:17.160
when life needs to change, we change.

00:33:18.079 --> 00:33:19.839
Sis, don't worry about it.

00:33:19.839 --> 00:33:21.799
If it's too much, we'll just buy new stuff.

00:33:22.000 --> 00:33:23.920
Alright, listen to Second Brother.

00:33:23.920 --> 00:33:24.640
No, no.

00:33:24.640 --> 00:33:26.480
Listen to General Manager Li.

00:33:32.079 --> 00:33:32.680
What's up?

00:33:33.680 --> 00:33:34.640
I'll buy you a soda.

00:33:35.480 --> 00:33:36.079
So nice of you.

00:33:36.079 --> 00:33:37.279
To soothe your wounded heart.

00:33:40.079 --> 00:33:41.039
Open it yourself.

00:33:45.759 --> 00:33:46.319
By the way,

00:33:47.079 --> 00:33:48.440
has my money trouble

00:33:48.799 --> 00:33:49.880
already spread around?

00:33:50.440 --> 00:33:51.240
Yeah.

00:33:51.599 --> 00:33:52.960
Haven't you heard the saying?

00:33:52.960 --> 00:33:54.960
Good news stays home, bad news travels far.

00:33:55.720 --> 00:33:57.279
Some say you're bankrupt.

00:33:57.279 --> 00:33:59.599
Some say you're suspected of money laundering.

00:33:59.599 --> 00:34:01.440
And some say you ran off with the money.

00:34:03.160 --> 00:34:05.160
Is that the image I have in your minds?

00:34:06.000 --> 00:34:08.079
You think you're some great guy?

00:34:11.719 --> 00:34:14.159
They really aren't including you anymore.

00:34:15.119 --> 00:34:16.440
I'm the one not playing with them.

00:34:17.519 --> 00:34:19.679
Even the ducks in Uncle Wang's kitchen aren't as stubborn as you.

00:34:20.559 --> 00:34:23.079
They're okay for small-time stuff,

00:34:23.079 --> 00:34:24.079
but for real big things,

00:34:24.079 --> 00:34:24.960
they can't handle it.

00:34:25.400 --> 00:34:27.320
You just love being sarcastic.

00:34:27.800 --> 00:34:29.599
Now you're just waiting to see them fail?

00:34:30.119 --> 00:34:32.559
Trust me, you won't have to wait long.

00:34:34.079 --> 00:34:35.760
I'm saying, you...

00:34:36.559 --> 00:34:38.280
You clearly care about them a lot.

00:34:38.280 --> 00:34:40.760
Why can't you just get along?

00:34:41.360 --> 00:34:42.480
Go ask them.

00:34:44.280 --> 00:34:45.760
Always, constantly,

00:34:45.760 --> 00:34:47.079
secretly keeping tabs on them.

00:34:47.079 --> 00:34:48.079
Don't think I don't know.

00:34:53.639 --> 00:34:55.280
When are you taking me antiquing?

00:34:55.280 --> 00:34:56.360
You've said it many times.

00:34:57.440 --> 00:34:58.440
In a few more days.

00:34:58.760 --> 00:35:00.039
Things have been busy lately.

00:35:00.800 --> 00:35:01.960
No integrity.

00:35:02.280 --> 00:35:03.239
Unreliable.

00:35:04.199 --> 00:35:05.519
No wonder they don't include you.

00:35:15.519 --> 00:35:16.960
Qiu'er, and you too.

00:35:17.320 --> 00:35:18.760
Since we're running a business,

00:35:18.760 --> 00:35:20.679
I hope you'll take it seriously and do it well.

00:35:20.679 --> 00:35:21.079
Yes.

00:35:21.079 --> 00:35:22.760
Don't be greedy and keep looking for more.

00:35:22.880 --> 00:35:24.880
The restaurant's future supply channels,

00:35:24.880 --> 00:35:25.719
including promotion,

00:35:25.719 --> 00:35:26.719
you'll need to oversee.

00:35:26.719 --> 00:35:27.280
Yes.

00:35:27.719 --> 00:35:28.840
So I think...

00:35:28.840 --> 00:35:30.760
you should quit your bank job.

00:35:33.000 --> 00:35:34.719
Quit? Why quit?

00:35:34.719 --> 00:35:36.400
Such a big deal just came in.

00:35:36.400 --> 00:35:37.400
If I quit now, this...

00:35:37.519 --> 00:35:38.159
this thing...

00:35:38.159 --> 00:35:39.039
It's fine, Qiu'er.

00:35:39.039 --> 00:35:40.880
Once this money reaches you,

00:35:40.880 --> 00:35:41.880
won't that count as your performance?

00:35:41.880 --> 00:35:42.480
Yes.

00:35:42.480 --> 00:35:43.760
Right? The bank can't just ignore you.

00:35:43.760 --> 00:35:44.039
Yes.

00:35:44.039 --> 00:35:46.079
They'll give you the bonus you deserve, won't they?

00:35:46.079 --> 00:35:47.159
Yes, yes, yes.

00:35:47.159 --> 00:35:47.840
Right?

00:35:47.880 --> 00:35:48.840
Even though you say that,

00:35:48.840 --> 00:35:50.480
but... quitting... this...

00:35:50.599 --> 00:35:51.760
It won't be a problem.

00:35:52.079 --> 00:35:53.559
But for me, it's just...

00:35:53.599 --> 00:35:56.199
My daily expenses, I...

00:35:56.199 --> 00:35:58.079
Your salary won't be less.

00:35:58.079 --> 00:35:59.679
There's also a monthly entertainment budget.

00:35:59.920 --> 00:36:01.719
Treat clients when needed.

00:36:01.719 --> 00:36:02.960
Have meals when needed.

00:36:03.159 --> 00:36:04.159
It'll all be reimbursed.

00:36:04.159 --> 00:36:05.000
Isn't that enough?

00:36:07.559 --> 00:36:09.480
Fine, then I'll quit, I'll quit.

00:36:09.480 --> 00:36:10.519
Hurry up and thank your Second Brother.

00:36:10.519 --> 00:36:12.039
See? See? See? Enough, right?

00:36:12.039 --> 00:36:14.320
My Second Brother is indeed rich and powerful.

00:36:14.320 --> 00:36:16.119
Your little brother is deeply impressed.

00:36:16.360 --> 00:36:17.159
Just work hard.

00:36:17.159 --> 00:36:17.840
Alright, I... I'll do this.

00:36:17.840 --> 00:36:18.679
Then I'll think it over properly.

00:36:18.679 --> 00:36:19.840
Otherwise, I'll just quit.

00:36:19.920 --> 00:36:21.880
Running back and forth so many kilometers every day,

00:36:21.880 --> 00:36:23.559
only a fool would do that, right?

00:36:42.519 --> 00:36:43.280
Old Tong.

00:36:43.719 --> 00:36:45.000
The documents are all verified.

00:36:51.119 --> 00:36:52.840
No problem.

00:36:53.280 --> 00:36:54.639
Thanks, Ranran.

00:36:56.000 --> 00:36:57.519
Old Tong, oh Old Tong.

00:36:57.519 --> 00:37:00.719
You really amazed us all with this one.

00:37:00.719 --> 00:37:02.039
This deal...

00:37:02.360 --> 00:37:03.519
...is really huge.

00:37:03.519 --> 00:37:04.559
It's alright.

00:37:06.360 --> 00:37:08.480
Old Tong, you've hit the jackpot.

00:37:08.480 --> 00:37:10.199
You snatched the corporate manager's work.

00:37:10.199 --> 00:37:11.239
Thanks, Ranran.

00:37:11.920 --> 00:37:14.039
Which big shot did you hook up with?

00:37:14.039 --> 00:37:16.000
Really? They've got some serious clout.

00:37:16.000 --> 00:37:17.280
We underestimated you before.

00:37:17.280 --> 00:37:18.320
Congratulations.

00:37:18.320 --> 00:37:19.320
This isn't much.

00:37:19.320 --> 00:37:20.800
It's just our roast duck restaurant.

00:37:20.800 --> 00:37:22.159
We got some investment.

00:37:22.480 --> 00:37:25.039
There will be more later.

00:37:25.039 --> 00:37:25.960
But, um...

00:37:25.960 --> 00:37:27.800
Wait... wait until the roast duck restaurant opens.

00:37:27.800 --> 00:37:29.599
I'll treat everyone to roast duck there.

00:37:29.599 --> 00:37:30.480
For real?

00:37:30.480 --> 00:37:31.039
For real, for real.

00:37:31.039 --> 00:37:32.079
That's some serious strength.

00:37:32.079 --> 00:37:33.159
But let's be honest.

00:37:33.159 --> 00:37:34.800
When the time comes, you have to bring your friends...

00:37:34.800 --> 00:37:36.320
...and your clients over to our place.

00:37:36.320 --> 00:37:37.599
We have private rooms and everything.

00:37:37.599 --> 00:37:38.880
Brought... brought some souvenirs.

00:37:38.880 --> 00:37:40.000
No problem, no problem.

00:37:40.159 --> 00:37:41.719
Brother Tong, you've got style.

00:37:41.719 --> 00:37:42.800
It's nothing, it's nothing.

00:37:43.000 --> 00:37:43.559
Help yourselves.

00:37:43.559 --> 00:37:44.199
Thanks, brother.

00:37:44.519 --> 00:37:45.559
Put it away, put it away.

00:37:45.559 --> 00:37:46.880
There are only five, only five.

00:37:47.000 --> 00:37:48.440
We're waiting for your roast duck!

00:38:27.440 --> 00:38:28.199
President Liu.

00:38:28.800 --> 00:38:29.480
Just a moment.

00:38:37.840 --> 00:38:38.880
Why are you closing the door?

00:38:39.920 --> 00:38:42.679
I have something to tell you, it's just...

00:38:43.000 --> 00:38:44.480
It's just that...

00:38:44.559 --> 00:38:47.480
I'm very grateful for your trust all these years...

00:38:47.480 --> 00:38:49.360
...and for your care and guidance.

00:38:49.719 --> 00:38:51.320
After some consideration...

00:38:51.320 --> 00:38:52.199
I want to...

00:38:52.760 --> 00:38:53.800
I know.

00:38:54.960 --> 00:38:55.920
Old Tong.

00:38:58.119 --> 00:38:59.039
I know.

00:38:59.880 --> 00:39:02.119
About transferring you to Mentougou...

00:39:02.239 --> 00:39:03.360
...you have some thoughts on that.

00:39:05.280 --> 00:39:06.079
It just so happens...

00:39:06.760 --> 00:39:08.679
I spoke with President Chen on the phone.

00:39:09.159 --> 00:39:10.519
Regarding your recent performance...

00:39:10.519 --> 00:39:11.719
...we exchanged some views.

00:39:12.559 --> 00:39:15.079
We feel you're not quite adapting over there.

00:39:15.079 --> 00:39:17.360
So after thinking about it, I decided...

00:39:17.599 --> 00:39:19.000
...to transfer you back early.

00:39:20.639 --> 00:39:22.679
To transfer you back early.

00:39:24.599 --> 00:39:26.079
I heard from Xiao Jia.

00:39:26.440 --> 00:39:28.880
You just brought in a big deal for our bank.

00:39:28.880 --> 00:39:30.239
This is what an old employee...

00:39:30.239 --> 00:39:31.599
...should be achieving.

00:39:32.440 --> 00:39:35.320
I heard there will be more income from this deal.

00:39:41.719 --> 00:39:43.800
Good, good job.

00:39:43.800 --> 00:39:44.639
Old Tong.

00:39:44.800 --> 00:39:45.880
You see?

00:39:45.880 --> 00:39:47.639
Sending you to the grassroots for training...

00:39:47.639 --> 00:39:49.079
...it's only been a few days...

00:39:49.159 --> 00:39:50.800
...and the results are remarkable.

00:39:51.320 --> 00:39:52.079
This, this, this...

00:39:53.440 --> 00:39:54.800
What does this show?

00:39:55.119 --> 00:39:57.320
It shows you have potential.

00:39:57.719 --> 00:39:59.599
But you have to be hard on yourself.

00:39:59.599 --> 00:40:01.880
You have to diligently tap into your potential.

00:40:02.000 --> 00:40:03.360
Right, right, yes, yes.

00:40:03.360 --> 00:40:04.239
No, no, no.

00:40:04.239 --> 00:40:04.880
That's not...

00:40:04.880 --> 00:40:07.039
I still appreciate your mentoring, it's just...

00:40:07.360 --> 00:40:07.920
However...

00:40:07.920 --> 00:40:10.079
I... I feel I... I...

00:40:11.400 --> 00:40:15.440
Our bank has always been clear about rewards and punishments.

00:40:15.960 --> 00:40:18.159
Your previous performance had shortcomings.

00:40:18.159 --> 00:40:19.599
So we sent you down for training.

00:40:19.599 --> 00:40:20.920
To improve your professional level.

00:40:21.360 --> 00:40:23.000
Now that your ability has improved...

00:40:23.000 --> 00:40:24.079
...and your performance is outstanding...

00:40:24.320 --> 00:40:26.119
...naturally, the rewards must keep up.

00:40:26.480 --> 00:40:29.239
The five percent commission I promised you before...

00:40:29.639 --> 00:40:30.880
...will be added next month.

00:40:33.599 --> 00:40:34.840
But Old Tong.

00:40:35.239 --> 00:40:36.679
As a veteran employee...

00:40:37.119 --> 00:40:39.039
...besides having outstanding performance yourself...

00:40:39.159 --> 00:40:40.920
...you must also for other employees...

00:40:40.920 --> 00:40:42.719
...act as a role model.

00:40:43.679 --> 00:40:46.079
I hope that after you transfer back this time...

00:40:46.320 --> 00:40:48.760
...you will stay humble and keep up the good work.

00:41:00.280 --> 00:41:01.400
Is there anything else?

00:41:05.239 --> 00:41:06.840
Look how this turned out.

00:41:06.840 --> 00:41:07.760
This is really...

00:41:11.840 --> 00:41:13.480
It's nothing, nothing.

00:41:13.599 --> 00:41:14.639
Nothing, nothing.

00:41:14.800 --> 00:41:16.320
You're busy, thank you.

00:41:17.000 --> 00:41:18.159
You're busy, you're busy.

00:41:19.360 --> 00:41:20.280
No need to close the door.

00:41:20.440 --> 00:41:21.480
Okay, okay.

00:41:23.559 --> 00:41:24.559
Don't close it, don't close it.

00:41:27.039 --> 00:41:27.920
You're busy, you're busy.